OL,3,CO'Neill offers apology for 'all lives
OL,4,Clost during conflict'
OL,6,FSinn Fein's Michelle O'Neill has
OL,7,Freiterated her apology for all lives
OL,8,Flost during the Troubles after the
OL,9,FOperation Kenova report was published.
OL,11,FThe report looked into the actions of
OL,12,Fthe Army's top spy in Northern
OL,13,FIreland, codenamed Stakeknife during
OL,14,Fthe conflict.
OL,16,FThe report called for the UK
OL,17,FGovernment and republican leadership
OL,18,Fto apologise for failing to prevent
OL,19,Fthe torture and killings of suspected
OL,20,Finformers.
