OL,3,CO'Neill offers apology for 'all lives
OL,4,Clost during conflict'
OL,6,F"My heartfelt thoughts are with all
OL,7,Fthose families whose loved ones were
OL,8,Fkilled, whose anguish, whose hurt,
OL,9,Fwhose loss continues to be felt very
OL,10,Fdeeply.
OL,12,F"The injustices and tragedies of the
OL,13,Fpast have left a deep legacy of
OL,14,Fsuffering and trauma right across or
OL,15,Fsociety.
OL,17,F"We must never forget those who have
OL,18,Fdied or been injured and their
OL,19,Ffamilies.
