OL,6,FDUP leader Sir Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,7,Fquestioned whether the #40million
OL,8,Fspent on the investigation could have
OL,9,Fbeen better spent resourcing policing
OL,10,Fin Northern Ireland.
OL,12,F"The work of the police, army or the
OL,13,Fsecurity services was a just cause.
OL,14,FTheir job was to undermine
OL,15,Fterrorists," he said.
