OL,3,CO'Neill offers apology for 'all lives
OL,4,Clost during conflict'
OL,6,F"The fact that the security services
OL,7,Fhad so many agents working at the top
OL,8,Fof the PIRA, is testament to their
OL,9,Fsuccess. Whilst having lessons to
OL,10,Flearn for the government, the report
OL,11,Freminds us that the intelligence
OL,12,Fagencies had infiltrated the PIRA to
OL,13,Fsuch an extent that they rendered the
OL,14,Forganisation almost inoperable.
OL,16,F"Working within the security forces
OL,17,Fwas a role of honour in the Troubles.
