OL,3,CO'Neill offers apology for 'all lives
OL,4,Clost during conflict'
OL,6,F"#40 million is a huge bill to
OL,7,Finvestigate the activities of one
OL,8,Fagent in the PIRA. It begs the
OL,9,Fquestion if that money might have been
OL,10,Fbetter spent on proactive policing
OL,11,Ftoday. It is even more disappointing
OL,12,Fthat on the back of such an expensive
OL,13,Finvestigation, the PPS has failed to
OL,14,Fsecure a single prosecution.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
