OL,6,FA Number 10 spokeswoman said: "We
OL,7,Fwould want to extend our deepest
OL,8,Fsympathies with all the families who
OL,9,Flost loved ones during this very dark
OL,10,Fperiod in Northern Ireland and it's
OL,11,Fimportant we do not forget the
OL,12,Fthousands of victims, their families
OL,13,Fand neighbours from all communities
OL,14,Fwho have suffered as a result.
OL,16,F"On this interim report, it would not
OL,17,Fbe right to comment on the substance
OL,18,Fof it while it is an interim report.
