OL,6,F"We will respond in full in due course
OL,7,Ffollowing the full and final report
OL,8,Fand also following the conclusion of
OL,9,Flitigation which is related to the
OL,10,Fsubstance of this report."
OL,12,FStakeknife was part of the terror
OL,13,Fgroup's internal security unit - known
OL,14,Fas the 'nutting squad' - and Kenova
OL,15,Fexamined crimes such as murder and
OL,16,Ftorture, and the role played by the
OL,17,Fsecurity services, including MI5.
