OL,6,FThe agent Stakeknife was widely
OL,7,Fbelieved to be west Belfast man
OL,8,FFreddie Scappaticci, who was in his
OL,9,F70s when he died last year.
OL,11,FThe interim findings of Operation
OL,12,FKenova were revealed after an
OL,13,Finvestigation lasting seven years and
OL,14,Fcosting approximately #40 million.
