OL,6,FIt found those responsible for
OL,7,Fkillings were allowed to remain free
OL,8,Fto continue with their terrorist
OL,9,Factivities. The report found there
OL,10,Fshould have been 'alarm bells' ringing
OL,11,Fwithin those security organisations
OL,12,Fresponsible.
OL,14,FIt said claims Stakeknife saved
OL,15,F'hundreds of lives' were unjustified.
OL,16,FAnd the agent carried out countless
OL,17,Fattacks and killings. It said lives
OL,18,Fsaved by the activities of the agent
OL,19,Fwould have been in low figures.
